data.description: **** Seller's are open to all offers & offering $10,000 in sellers concessions for buying down your interest rate (which could significantly lower your monthly payment ) or help with closing costs**** Come take a look at this well maintained Mill Creek Crossing home!! In the coveted Navarro ISD, this lovely home boasts tile floors in the main living areas and comfortable carpeting in the bedrooms. The primary bedroom is tucked away for extra privacy and has a luxurious soaking tub to relax in and a seperate shower. The remainder of the 3 bedrooms are ample size and one of the bedrooms could even be a mother in law suite as it has a full bathroom right next to it in the hallway! The kitchen features granite countertops, a generously-sized island, and opens up to the living room for easy entertaining. In the backyard you will find an extended covered patio with plenty of room to relax, and beautiful oak trees. Situated on Hwy 46 between Seguin and New Braunfels, close to  the IH-10 and IH-35 corridors, and a short distance from the I30 toll road, this home is perfect for the commuter. Don't hesitate to make this your new home!
